snippet.title: PIANISTA: The Legendary Virtuoso - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Beautifully tuned music and marvelous technique awaits. PIANISTA: The Legendary Virtuoso is a high-end piano music game for Nintendo Switch. Check out 23 greatest composers, challenge 77 songs with 693 patterns in 3 different play modes. Designed perfectly for Joy-con, and supports 8 languages for global ranking.
